'''Zendesk Inc.'''是一家美国[[顾客服务|顾客服务]]软件公司，总部位于美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[旧金山|旧金山]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Zendesk Masters Customer Service|url=http://www.cmswire.com/cms/customer-experience/Zendesk-masters-customer-service-026626.php|accessdate=9 May 2016|author=DeFrancesco|date=25 September 2014|first=Robert|publisher=CMS Wire|archive-date=2020-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025185245/https://www.cmswire.com/cms/customer-experience/zendesk-masters-customer-service-026626.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Zendesk于2007年在[[丹麦|丹麦]][[哥本哈根|哥本哈根]]成立<ref name="ZendeskPress">{{Cite web|title=Zendesk Announces Third Quarter 2016 Results|url=https://www.zendesk.com/company/press/zendesk-announces-third-quarter-2016-results/|accessdate=21 November 2016|date=1 November 2016|publisher=Zendesk|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514000951/https://www.zendesk.com/company/press/zendesk-announces-third-quarter-2016-results/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=About Zendesk|url=https://www.zendesk.com/company/press/#about|accessdate=21 November 2016|publisher=Zendesk|archive-date=2021-06-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210608012819/https://www.zendesk.com/company/press/#about|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年4月，它收购了位于新加坡的即时聊天软件供应商{{link-en|Zopim}}<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.zendesk.com/company/press/zendesk-acquires-live-chat-leader-zopim/ |title=Zendesk Acquires Live Chat Leader Zopim |date=10 April 2014 |publisher=Zendesk |access-date=9 May 2016 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226224705/https://www.zendesk.com/company/press/zendesk-acquires-live-chat-leader-zopim/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name = "Zopim May2016">{{cite web |url=https://www.zendesk.com/company/press/zendesk-introduces-zopim-premium-live-chat-larger-teams/ |title=Zendesk Introduces Zopim Premium Live Chat for Larger Teams |date=16 April 2015 |publisher=Zendesk |access-date=9 May 2016 |archive-date=2020-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412140903/https://www.zendesk.com/company/press/zendesk-introduces-zopim-premium-live-chat-larger-teams/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。通過收购Zopim，Zendesk开始向[[人工智能|人工智能]]聊天领域进军。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Best Chatbot Software for Your Business {{!}} Zendesk Chatbot|url=https://www.zendesk.com/chat/chatbot/|access-date=2020-06-17|website=Zendesk|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125115326/https://www.zendesk.com/chat/chatbot/|dead-url=no}}</ref>該公司於2014年5月在[[纽约证券交易所|纽约证券交易所]]上市<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mercurynews.com/business/ci_25763611/Zendesk-prices-ipo-at-9-share-brings-100facts |title=Zendesk prices IPO at $9 a share, brings in $100 million |last=Owens |first=Jeremy C. |date=15 May 2014 |publisher=Mercury News |access-date=9 May 2016 |archive-date=2016-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160822191445/http://www.mercurynews.com/business/ci_25763611/Zendesk-prices-ipo-at-9-share-brings-100facts |dead-url=no }}</ref>，股票代码为ZEN，是罗素2000指数的成份股<ref>{{Cite web|title=Zendesk Inc (ZEN) Jumps 8.93% on February 17|url=https://www.equities.com/news/Zendesk-inc-zen-jumps-8-93-on-february-17|accessdate=9 May 2016|author=Equities Staff|date=17 February 2016|publisher=Equities.com|archive-date=2019-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190803180534/https://www.equities.com/news/Zendesk-inc-zen-jumps-8-93-on-february-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

